h%20law%2C%20they'd%20have%20to%20prove%20fault%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20there's%20much%20prospect%20of%20anyone%20proving%20fault%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Davies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBad%20weather%20at%20sea%20is%20not%20at%20all%20unexpected%2C%20which%20is%20why%20you%20can't%20just%20simply%20say%20bad%20weather%20and%20hope%20to%20get%20off%20the%20hook%2C%26quot%3B%20Davies%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20seems%20different%20about%20this%20case%20is%20that%20it%20came%20suddenly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20said%20Oregon-based%20maritime%20lawyer%20Gordon%20Carey%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20spell%20defeat%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20potential%20legal%20claim%20%26quot%3Bjust%20because%20it's%20a%20weather%20event.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22263a06c2-cf3c-4cfa-b1f9-87e01f3a92e2%5C%22%3EThe%20yacht%20was%20carrying%2022%2C%20including%20UK%20tech%20tycoon%20Mike%20Lynch%20and%20a%20Morgan%20Stanley%20exec%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20British-registered%20184-foot%20yacht%20was%20anchored%20about%20a%20half-mile%20off%20the%20Italian%20port%20of%20Porticello%20near%20Palermo%2C%20Sicily%2C%20and%20carrying%2022%20people%2C%20including%20UK%20tech%20tycoon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmike-lynch-missing-tech-tycoon-codefendant-died-before-yacht-sank-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMike%20Lynch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20when%20a%20fierce%20storm%20hit%20and%20quickly%20sank%20the%20vessel%20just%20after%204%20a.m.%20on%20Monday%2C%20according%20to%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20body%20of%20the%20yacht's%20chef%2C%20Recaldo%20Thomas%2C%20was%20found%20on%20Monday.%20Six%20other%20passengers%20%E2%80%94%20Lynch%3B%20his%2018-year-old%20daughter%20Hannah%3B%20Lynch's%20friend%20and%20Morgan%20Stanley%20International%20chairman%20Jonathan%20Bloomer%3B%20Bloomer's%20wife%2C%20Judy%3B%20Lynch's%20attorney%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmike-lynch-lawyer-christopher-morvillo-wife-dead-