nt%20posted%20to%20its%20website%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20can%20%26quot%3Bconfirm%20that%20the%20vessel%20encountered%20severe%20weather%20conditions%20and%20subsequently%20sank%20near%20Palermo%2C%20Italy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20a%20total%20of%2010%20crew%20members%20and%2012%20guests%20on%20board%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20priority%20is%20assisting%20with%20the%20ongoing%20search%20and%20providing%20all%20necessary%20support%20to%20the%20rescued%20passengers%20and%20crew%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20immediately%20clear%20who%20the%20captain%20and%20crew%20of%20the%20vessel%20were%20employed%20by.%20Camper%20%26amp%3B%20Nicholsons%20declined%20to%20comment%20beyond%20the%20statement%20posted%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20maritime%20legal%20experts%20BI%20spoke%20to%20said%20that%20the%20operator%20of%20the%20Bayesian%20could%20potentially%20face%20liability%20claims%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20circumstances%2C%20if%20it%20hired%20the%20captain%20and%20crew%20and%20managed%20the%20vessel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavies%20said%20a%20boat%20like%20the%20Bayesian%20is%20bound%20to%20have%20%26quot%3Ball%20kinds%20of%20insurance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20someone%20may%20make%20a%20claim%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20getting%20some%20money%20from%20the%20insurance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c753b0d3-8140-4158-a5e3-35810237acc1%5C%22%3EEnglish%20law%20would%20likely%20apply%20if%20any%20claims%20were%20made%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Davies%2C%20it%20is%20more%20likely%20that%20English%20law%20would%20apply%20should%20the%20family%20of%20any%20of%20the%20victims%20or%20a%20survivor%20try%20to%20take%20legal%20action%20since%20the%20yacht%20was%20a%20UK-flagged%20vessel.%20US%20law%20could%20be%20applied%20if%20jurisdiction%20could%20be%20established%2C%20said%20Davies%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20US%20law%2C%20crew%20members%2C%20not%20passengers%2C%20could%20potentially%20make%20an%20%26quot%3Bunseaworthiness%26quot%3B%20claim%2C%20according%20to%20the%20maritime%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20advantage%20of%20unseaworthiness%20is%20it's%20a%20strict%20liability%20claim%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sturley.%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20have%20to%20prove%20negligence.%20For%20other%20losses%2C%20you'd%20have%20to%20prove%20negligence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20an%20unseaworthiness%20claim%2C%20Davies%20explained%2C%20%26quot%3Byou'd%20have%20to%20argue%20that%20there's%20something%20about%20the%20vessel%20that%20makes%20it%20unfit%20to%20withstand%20a%20sudden%20storm%20like%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20find%20it%20hard%20to%20see%20there%20was%20any%20unseaworthiness%20of%20the%20vessel%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20under%20US%20law%2C%20the%20families%20of%20the%20dead%20could%20potentially%20make%20a%20legal%20claim%20under%20the%20Death%20on%20the%20High%20Seas%20Act%2C%20the%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20supposed%20to%20take%20precautions%20against%20weather%2C%20but%20you%20take%20precautions%20that%20are%20reasonable%20under%20the%20circumstances%2C%20and%20sometimes%20you%20have%20a%20freak%20weather%20event%20that%20nobody%20could%20see%20coming%2C%20and%20it%20would%20not%20have%20been%20reasonable%20to%20have%20guarded%20against%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Sturley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BNobody%20prepares%20for%20hurricanes%20in%20the%20Sahara%20Desert.%20And%20if%20a%20hurricane%20happens%20to%20hit%20the%20Sahara%20Desert%2C%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20people%20who%20didn't%20guard%20against%20it%20were%20negligent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fyacht-bayesian-lynch-sicily-waterspout-missing-sinking-7eb9496d2f22f85b82e9cfccaa397657%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Italian%20civil%20protection%20officials%20believe%20that%20a%20tornado-like%20waterspout%20hit%20where%20the%20yacht%20was%20anchored%2C%20likely%20causing%20it%20to%20capsize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it%20was%20a%20water%20spout%2C%20which%20it%20appears%20to%20be%2C%20it's%20what%20I%20would%20class%20as%20like%20a%20'black%20swan'%20event%2C%26quot%3B%20Matthew%20Schanck%2C%20chair%20of%20the%20UK-based%20Maritime%20Search%20and%20Rescue%20Council%20told%20the%20AP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbayesian-yacht-tragedy-legal-claims-likely-italy-sicily-experts-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724276610000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c6417db4912df3ae1d8ce0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbayesian-yacht-tragedy-legal-claims-likely-italy-sicily-experts-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maritime%20legal%20experts%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20operator%20behind%20the%20now-sunken%20luxury%20sailing%20yacht%2C%20the%20Bayesian%2C%20should%20lawyer%20up.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nmusumeci%40businessinsider.com%20(Natalie%20Musumeci)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A203%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbayesian-yacht-tragedy-legal-claims-likely-italy-sicily-experts-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I've%20been%20on%20dozens%20of%20cruises%2C%20and%20I've%20learned%20to%20avoid%206%20spending%20traps%20that%20drive%20up%20the%20bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20changed%20since%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%20See%20our%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-money-cruises-avoiding-spending-traps-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20current%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAffiliate%20links%20for%20the%20products%20on%20this%20page%20are%20from%20partners%20that%20compensate%20us%20(see%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Four-partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvertiser%20disclosure%20with%20our%20list%20of%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details).%20However%2C%20our%20opinions%20are%20our%20own.%20See%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftravel-insurance%2Fmethodology%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20travel%20insurance%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20write%20unbiased%20product%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22credit%20cards%20Holly%20Johnson%20Bahamas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c4ffb75da406397bf75de6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20Holly%20Johnson.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Holly%20Johnson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20love%20going%20on%20cruises%2C%20because%20the%20whole%20cost%20of%20my%20vacation%20is%20in%20a%20single%20fee.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20I%20still%20take%20care%20to%20avoid%20overspending%20on%20things%20like%20shopping%20and%20spa%20treatments.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFor%20emergencies%2C%20I%20have%20an%20annual%20travel%20insurance%20policy%20protecting%20me.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20say%20booking%20a%20cruise%20is%20like%20buying%20a%20%26quot%3Bvacation%20in%20a%20box%2C%26quot%3B%20mostly%20because%20the%20cruise%20fare%20includes%20lodging%2C%20transportation%2C%20food%2C%20and%20most%20of%20your%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20cruising%20also%20comes%20with%20its%20share%20of%20hidden%20costs%20that%20you%20have%20to%20know%20about%20and%20plan%20for%2C%20including%20the%20cost%20of%20things%20to%20do%20in%20port%2C%20cruise%20ship%20gratuities%20you%20typically%20pay%20at%20the%20end%20of%20your%20cruise%2C%20and%20whatever%20money%20you%20wind%20up%20losing%20in%20your%20ship's%20onboard%20casino.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftravel-insurance%2Fbest-cruise-travel-insurance-companies%5C%22%3ECruise%20travel%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20help%20cover%20emergency%20costs%20as%20well%2C%20which%20is%20why%20I%20have%20an%20annual%20travel%20insurance%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20quite%20a%20few%20spending%20traps%20to%20be%20aware%20of%2C%20which%20I%20have%20learned%20during%20the%20dozens%20of%20journeys%20I%20have%20taken%20with%20Carnival%2C%20Princess%2C%20Virgin%20Voyages%2C%20and%20MSC%20Cruises%20throughout%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%20When%20I'm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-budgeting-apps%5C%22%3Ebudgeting%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20cruises%2C%20I%20watch%20out%20for%20these%20six%20spending%20traps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20ATM%20fees%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%20off%2C%20I%20always%20get%20the%20cash%20I%20need%20from%20home%20before%20I%20take%20a%20cruise%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20or%20Europe%20especially.%20Why%3F%20Because%20the%20alternative%20is%20getting%20cash%20at%20whatever%20ATM%20you%20can%20find%20in%20port%20during%20a%20cruise%2C%20which%20will%20almost%20certainly%20charge%20high%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbank-atm-fees%5C%22%3EATM%20fees%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20cruisers%20seem%20to%20think%20they%20won't%20need%20any%20cash%20during%20their%20sailing%2C%20but%20they%20quickly%20discover%20they%20want%20to%20tip%20someone%20for%20excellent%20service%20on%20the%20ship%2C%20or%20they%20need%20money%20for%20a%20taxi%20or%20street%20food%20when%20they%20get%20off%20the%20ship%20for%20a%20few%20hours%20in%20port.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20lot%20easier%20to%20have%20this%20money%20with%20you%20ahead%20of%20time%2C%20so%20that's%20exactly%20what%20I%20do.%20For%20Caribbean%20cruises%20in%20particular%2C%20this%20part%20is%20easy%20since%20almost%20all%20spots%20in%20and%20around%20cruise%20ports%20accept%20US%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20Drinks%20(if%20you%20drink%20a%20lot)%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20drink%3Cem%3E%20a%20lot%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20cruises%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20just%20talking%20about%20cocktails%20and%20beer.%20I%20can't%20live%20without%20Coke%20Zero%20and%20lattes%20either%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20skip%20out%20on%20my%20favorite%20beverages%20(or%20all%20the%20caffeine%20I%20need)%20on%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20I%20always%20have%20a%20drink%20package%20when%20I%20cruise%2C%20which%20is%20easy%20since%20I%20normally%20cruise%20with%20MSC%20Cruises.%20Not%20only%20does%20the%20cruise%20line%20offer%20constant%20%26quot%3Bfree%20drinks%20and%20WiFi%26quot%3B%20packages%20that%20let%20you%20enjoy%20endless%20basic%20alcoholic%20beverages%2C%20soft%20drinks%2C%20coffees%2C%20and%20more%2C%20but%20I%20frequently%20book%20in%20the%20MSC%20Yacht%20Club%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20VIP%20%26quot%3Bship%20within%20a%20ship%26quot%3B%20comes%20with%20a%20premium%20drink%20package%20that%20works%20all%20over%20the%20vessel%2C%20so%20I%20can%20have%20endless%20cappuccinos%20and%20drink%20Aperol%20spritzes%20without%20worrying%20about%20a%20surprise%20bill.%20That's%20exactly%20what%20I%20plan%20to%20do%20on%20my%20next%20cruise%20in%20the%20Yacht%20Club%20on%20the%20MSC%20Seascape%2C%20which%20is%20the%20line's%20newest%20ship%20that%20sails%20out%20of%20Miami.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20Shopping%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECruise%20ships%20always%20have%20shops%20galore%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20offer%20anything%20you%20can't%20buy%20before%20your%20trip%20%E2%80%94%20usually%20at%20a%20lower%20cost.%20These%20stores%20will%20also%20try%20to%20entice%20you%20into%20visiting%20by%20offering%20a%20free%20gift%20that's%20usually%20something%20like%20an%20inexpensive%20necklace%20or%20a%20beach%20tote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20fall%20for%20it!%20If%20you%20get%20sucked%20into%20a%20store%2C%20you%20could%20wind%20up%20wasting%20valuable%20vacation%20time%20and%20some%20of%20your%20travel%20funds%20to%20boot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E4.%20Spa%20treatments%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20not%20against%20spa%20treatments%20on%20a%20cruise%20by%20any%20means%2C%20and%20I%20frequently%20get%20a%20message%20or%20relax%20in%20the%20thermal%20areas%20of%20the%20vessels%20I'm%20on.%20However%2C%20I%20never%20book%20spa%20treatments%20before%20a%20cruise%20or%20during%20the%20first%20few%20days%20of%20a%20journey%20since%20prices%20tend%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20higher%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20you%20cruise%20for%20a%20while%2C%20you%20quickly%20notice%20that%20cruise%20lines%20roll%20out%20all%20their%20best%20deals%20after%20the%20first%20few%20days%20of%20sailing.%20This%20often%20means%20you%20can%20book%20massages%20and%20other%20spa%20treatments%20for%20up%20to%2040%25%20off%2C%20which%20is%20a%20nice%20benefit%20if%20you're%20looking%20to%20save%20some%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E5.%20Too%20many%20excursions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20also%20learned%20to%20stop%20pre-booking%20and%20paying%20for%20so%20many%20excursions%2C%20especially%20when%20I'm%20traveling%20with%20my%20family%20of%20four.%20The%20more%20I%20cruise%2C%20the%20more%20I%20have%20found%20that%20my%20family%20really%20needs%20some%20downtime%20on%20a%20cruise%2C%20and%20that%20some%20group%20excursions%20are%20a%20lot%20more%20trouble%20than%20they're%20worth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20times%20lately%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20when%20we%20don't%20even%20get%20off%20the%20ship%2C%20or%20we%20just%20get%20off%20for%20a%20few%20hours%20to%20walk%20around.%20That%20seems%20to%20be%20more%20than%20enough%2C%20and%20we%20mix%20in%20a%20few%20organized%20excursions%20we're%20dead%20set%20on%20doing%20to%20mix%20things%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20ports%20where%20I%20just%20want%20to%20do%20something%20easy%2C%20so%20that's%20what%20we%20do.%20On%20my%20next%20Caribbean%20cruise%2C%20we've%20booked%20a%20resort%20day%20pass%20at%20an%20all-inclusive%20resort%20in%20Puerto%20Plata%2C%20Dominican%20Republic%20through%20a%20platform%20called%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.resortforaday.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResort%20for%20a%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20day%20at%20an%20all-inclusive%20resort%20includes%20beach%20time%2C%20a%20chair%2C%20towels%2C%20food%2C%20and%20drinks%20(including%20alcohol)%2C%20and%20it%20only%20set%20us%20back%20%2474%20per%20person.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20we%20only%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20a%20taxi%20ride%20there%20and%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E6.%20Under%20packing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20I%20have%20learned%20the%20hard%20way%20to%20bring%20all%20the%20toiletries%20and%20sunscreen%20we%20could%20possibly%20need%2C%20as%20well%20as%20remedies%20for%20seasickness%20and%20a%20first%20aid%20kit.%20The%20fact%20is%2C%20having%20to%20buy%20these%20items%20on%20a%20cruise%20ship%20or%20in%20a%20port%20can%20be%20overly%20expensive%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20get%20a%20lot%20to%20choose%20from%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20typically%20check%20a%20bag%20when%20I%20fly%20to%20my%20cruise%20departure%20destination%20for%20this%20reason%2C%20even%20if%20I%20have%20to%20pay%20checked%20bag%20fees%20to%20do%20so.%20After%20all%2C%20a%20%2430%20checked%20bag%20fee%20is%20nothing%20when%20you%20compare%20the%20costs%20of%20bringing%20sunscreen%20and%20medicines%20from%20home%20versus%20paying%20that%20much%20or%20more%20for%20a%20single%20can%20of%20sunblock%20on%20the%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20September%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20artic