tion%3EI%20thought%20the%20frosting%20on%20this%20doughnut%20was%20unnecessary.%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20double-chocolate%20doughnut%20was%20one%20of%20only%20two%20I%20tried%20that%20had%20Dunkin's%20chocolate-cake%20doughnut%20base.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20didn't%20think%20the%20chocolate%20frosting%20added%20any%20real%20diversity%20to%20the%20flavor%20and%20only%20served%20to%20make%20the%20doughnut%20sweeter%20and%20a%20bit%20messier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDunkin's%20Boston-kreme%20doughnut%20is%20a%20classic%20for%20a%20reason.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22672%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20doughnut%20with%20no%20hole%2C%20cut%20in%20half%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%20The%20doughnut%20is%20filled%20with%20cream%20and%20topped%20with%20chocolate%20icing.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c4b3b05da406397bf72f79%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Boston-kreme%20doughnut%20is%20filled%20with%20Dunkin's%20Bavarian%20cream.%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Boston-kreme%20doughnut%20is%20topped%20with%20a%20thick%20coating%20of%20chocolate%20icing%20and%20filled%20with%20Dunkin's%20Bavarian%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20classic%20combination%20for%20a%20reason%20%E2%80%94%20the%20warm%2C%20chocolate%20flavor%20of%20the%20icing%20pairs%20perfectly%20with%20the%20mild%2C%20velvety%20filling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%206-year-old%20was%20surprised%20that%20he%20liked%20the%20Boston-kreme%20flavor%20more%20than%20the%20double%20chocolate%2C%20as%20he%20usually%20prefers%20the%20most%20chocolatey%20dessert%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20powdered%20doughnut%20tasted%20fresh.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22578%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20doughnut%20topped%20with%20powdered%20sugar%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c4b40a5da406397bf72faf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22433%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20powdered%20sugar%20gave%20this%20doughnut%20a%20nostalgic%20appeal.%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20spots%20on%20this%20list%20all%20belong%20to%20simple%2C%20classic%20doughnuts.%20In%20three%20of%20the%20four%20cases%20%E2%80%94%20the%20powdered%20doughnut%20included%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20much%20I%20enjoyed%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cake-style%20powdered%20doughnut%20was%20soft%20and%20tasted%20fresh%2C%20and%20the%20powdered%20sugar%20gave%20it%20a%20nostalgic%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20old-fashioned%20doughnut%20was%20another%20pleasant%20surprise.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22601%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20plain%20cakey%20doughnut%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c4b565b4912df3ae1cf046%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22451%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20liked%20the%20simplicity%20of%20the%20old-fashioned%20doughnut.%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20figured%20the%20humdrum%20old-fashioned%20doughnut%20would%20land%20near%20the%20bottom%20of%20my%20ranking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20doughnuts%20I%20tried%2C%20and%20by%20far%20the%20biggest%20surprise%20%E2%80%94%20if%20it%20weren't%20for%20this%20taste%20test%2C%20I%20would've%20never%20chosen%20one%20myself.%20However%2C%20I%20really%20enjoyed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could've%20gone%20for%20more%20of%20the%20outer%20crunchiness%20of%20classic%2C%20deep-fried%20cake%20doughnuts.%20Still%2C%20this%20one%20felt%20well-suited%20for%20eating%20alongside%20(and%20occasionally%20dipping%20in)%20a%20hot%20cup%20of%20coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20glazed%20doughnut%20was%20simple%20but%20delicious.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22658%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20glazed%20doughnut%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c4b60c1aa2ac29ee32809e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22494%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20outer%20glaze%20added%20sweetness%20and%20flavor%20without%20overwhelming%20the%20doughnut.%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20what%20you're%20probably%20thinking%20%E2%80%94%20boring.%20But%20this%20big%2C%20soft%2C%20sweet%20doughnut%20was%20a%20stealth%20favorite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sweet%2C%20flaky%20outer%20glaze%20added%20sweetness%20and%20flavor%20without%20overwhelming%20the%20doughnut%20itself%20(which%20is%20something%20that%20was%20lost%20in%20the%20frosted%20options).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20glazed-chocolate%20doughnut%20was%20my%20favorite.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222199%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20chocolate-cake%20doughnut%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c4b670b4912df3ae1cf0f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221649%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20glazed-chocolate%20doughnut%20was%20the%20last%20one%20I%20tried.%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20admit%2C%20the%20winning%20flavor%20was%20no%20surprise.%20From%2040-plus%20years%20of%20doughnut-eating%20experience%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20the%20glazed-chocolate%20variety%20is%20among%20Dunkin's%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20final%20doughnut%20I%20tried%2C%20and%20after%20trying%2015%20flavors%2C%20I%20really%20wasn't%20in%20the%20mood%20for%20another.%20However%2C%20I%20ate%20the%20whole%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20normally%20a%20chocolate%20lover%2C%20but%20the%20chocolate-cake%20doughnut%20had%20only%20a%20mild%20cocoa%20flavor%2C%20a%20hearty%20cakiness%2C%20and%20just%20enough%20glaze%20to%20sweeten%20the%20whole%20thing%20up%20without%20making%20it%20taste%20too%20sugary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv