%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20decades%2C%20India's%20policy%20was%20to%20maintain%20distance%20from%20all%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20has%20now%20changed...%20Today%2C%20India's%20policy%20is%20to%20maintain%20close%20ties%20with%20all%20countries.%20Today's%20India%20wants%20to%20connect%20with%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20in%20a%20subtle%20jab%20at%20the%20Non-Aligned%20Movement%20of%20the%201970s%20under%20then%20Congress%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday's%20India%20is%20with%20everyone%20and%20thinks%20about%20everyone's%20benefit.%20Today%20the%20world%20respects%20India%20as%20Vishwa%20Bandhu%20(friend%20to%20all)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20years%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20been%20to%20several%20nations%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20one%20that%20made%20the%20biggest%20headlines%20being%20Israel.%20It%20acknowledged%20the%20shift%20in%20the%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20that%20was%20already%20in%20progress%20--%20from%20the%20traditional%20military-security%20paradigm%20to%20economic%20and%20developmental%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20visit%20to%20Poland%20underscores%20India's%20heightened%20participation%20in%20matters%20involving%20Europe%20and%20the%20middle-east.%20In%20both%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%20and%20Israel's%20war%20on%20Hamas%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20played%20the%20role%20of%20a%20peacemaker.%20He%20is%20expected%20to%20visit%20Ukraine%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20his%20departure%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20his%20visit%20marks%2070%20years%20of%20diplomatic%20relations%20with%20Poland%2C%20which%20is%20now%20also%20a%20%26quot%3Bkey%20economic%20partner%20in%20Central%20Europe%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20bilateral%20trade%20is%20substantial.%20And%20it's%20of%20the%20order%20of%20US%246%20billion%2C%20which%20makes%20Poland%20India's%20largest%20trading%20partner%20in%