0Kabaddi%20In%20PM%20Modi's%20Poland%20Speech%3A%20Top%20Quotes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThis%20scene%20is%20extraordinary.%20Ever%20since%20I%20landed%20here%2C%20you%20have%20not%20got%20tired%2C%20you%20have%20come%20here%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20Poland%2C%20and%20you%20speak%20a%20different%20language%20but%20you%20are%20connected%20with%20the%20spirit%20of%20Indianness.%20%C2%A0I%20thank%20you%20for%20the%20grand%20welcome%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BSince%20last%20week%2C%20the%20Indian%20media%20is%20only%20talking%20about%20you.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20headline%20that%20it's%20the%20first%20time%20in%2045%20years%20that%20an%20Indian%20PM%20is%20visiting%20Poland.%20A%20lot%20of%20good%20things%20are%20there%20in%20my%20fate.%20I%20visited%20Austria%20recently.%20There%20too%2C%20an%20Indian%20PM%20was%20visiting%20after%20four%20decades.%20Situations%20have%20changed%20now.%20For%20decades%2C%20India's%20policy%20was%20to%20maintain%20distance%20from%20all%20countries.%20Today%2C%20India's%20policy%20is%20to%20maintain%20close%20ties%20with%20all%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BFor%20India%2C%20it's%20not%20about%20geopolitics%2C%20it's%20about%20values.%20This%20is%20our%20legacy%20that%20fills%20every%20Indian%20with%20pride.%20Poland%20has%20been%20witness%20to%20India's%20'Sanatan%20bhava'.%20During%20World%20War%20II%20when%20Poland%20was%20going%20through%20a%20tough%20time%20and%20was%20seeking%20refuge%2C%20Jam%20Saheb%20came%20forward.%20He%20constructed%20a%20special%20camp%20for%20Polish%20women%20and%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BTwo%20decades%20ago%2C%20when%20an%20earthquake%20hit%20Gujarat%2C%20Jamnagar%20was%20affected%20badly.%20Poland%20was%20among%20the%20first%20countries%20to%20extend%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20Indians%20are%20known%20for%20their%20efforts%2C%20excellence%20and%20empathy.%20Wherever%20we%20go%2C%20we%20are%20seen%20putting%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20effort.%20In%20the%20whole%20world%2C%20we%20are%20known%20for%20excellence%2C%20be%20it%20it%20sector%20or%20our%20doctors%2C%20they%20are%20known%20for%20excellence.%20We%20are%20known%20for%20empathy%20as%20well%2C%20we%20%C2%A0are%20the%20first%20to%20extend%20help%20to%20countries%20going%20through%20crises.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20also%20the%20biggest%20endorser%20of%20peace.%20This%20is%20not%20an%20era%20of%20war.%20It's%20the%20time%20to%20unite%20against%20the%20forces%20that%20pose%20a%20danger%20to%20humankind.%20This%20is%20why%20India%20stresses%20diplomacy%20and%20dialogue%2F%20The%20way%20you%20helped%20Indian%20students%20stuck%20in%20Poland%20(during%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20War)%2C%20we%20saw%20that.%20You%20arranged%20langars%2C%20you%20opened%20your%20doors%2C%20Polish%20government%20removed%20visa%20requirements%20for%20our%20Indian%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWe%20sent%20medicines%20and%20vaccines%20to%20150%20countries.%20Whenever%20there%20is%20a%20natural%20disaster%20anywhere%2C%20the%20country's%20mantra%20is%20humanity%20first%2C%20if%20there%20is%20a%20war%2C%20India%20says%20humanity%20first.%20India%20always%20comes%20forward%20as%20first%20responder%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20many%20similarities%20between%20Indian%20and%20Polish%20societies.%20One%20of%20them%20is%20democracy.%20Indians%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20faith%20in%20it.%20We%20have%20seen%20that%20in%20Indian%20elections.%20The%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20were%20the%20biggest%20in%20the%20history%20of%20polls.%20The%20level%20of%20efficiency%20is%20a%20big%20strength%20of%20Indians%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20connected%20through%20the%20game%20of%20Kabaddi%20as%20well.%20This%20game%20reached%20Poland%20through%20India%20and%20they%20took%20it%20to%20great%20heights.%20Poland%20is%20going%20to%20host%20the%20Kabaddi%20championship%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20I%20want%20to%20wish%20good%20luck%20to%20their%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20in%20his%20address.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20taken%20financial%20inclusion%20to%20the%20next%20level.%20We%20opened%20500%20million%20Jan%20Dhan%20Bank%20accounts.%20In%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20India's%20broadband%20users%20have%20increased%20from%2060%20million%20to%20940%20million.%20If%20we%20combine%20the%20US%20and%20UK%20populations%2C%20the%20broadband%20users%20will%20come%20up%20to%20that.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724267940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Foi60men8_pm-modi_625x300_21_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthis-scene-is-extraordinary-top-quotes-from-pm-address-in-poland-6388752%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20addressed%20the%20Indian%20community%20in%20Poland%20today.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20the%20first%20Indian%20leader%20to%20visit%20the%20nation%20in%20over%20four%20decades%2C%20making%20it%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20visits%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20best%20cooling%20pajamas%20for%20curbing%20night%20sweats%2C%20tested%20by%20hot%20sleepers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221