20air%20strike%20destroyed%20their%20home%20in%20Deir%20al-Balah.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A304%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fclyn31g50e3o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fclyn31g50e3o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fclyn31g50e3o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Madhya%20Pradesh%20Women's%20Panel%20Defunct%20For%204%20Years%2C%2050%2C000%20Cases%20Pending%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20State%20Women's%20Commission%2C%20established%20to%20protect%20and%20empower%20women%2C%20has%20been%20left%20in%20a%20state%20of%20disarray%2C%20with%20more%20than%2050%2C000%20complaints%20pending%20and%20no%20one%20to%20hear%20them.%20The%20Commission%2C%20which%20has%20been%20defunct%20for%20years%2C%20has%20become%20a%20symbol%20of%20administrative%20neglect%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20visit%20to%20the%20Women's%20Commission%20office%20in%20Bhopal%20reveals%20a%20grim%20picture.%20In%20the%20parking%20lot%20stand%20vehicles%20covered%20in%20dust%2C%20marking%20the%20inactivity%20that%20has%20plagued%20the%20commission%20for%20years.%20Inside%2C%20piles%20of%20files%20are%20scattered%20everywhere%2C%20a%20few%20even%20hanging%20on%20the%20nameplate%20outside%20the%20chairperson's%20room%20--%20a%20room%20that%20has%20seen%20no%20occupant%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202020%2C%20the%20commission%20has%20had%20no%20benches%2C%20no%20staff%20and%20no%20chairperson%20to%20address%20the%20grievances%20of%20women%20across%20the%20state.%20The%20previous%20chairperson%2C%20Shobha%20Ojha%2C%20was%20appointed%20by%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Kamal%20Nath%20just%20before%20his%20government%20collapsed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20appointment%2C%20along%20with%20those%20of%20other%20members%20was%20cancelled%20by%20the%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20government%2C%20which%20held%20them%20unconstitutional.%20The%20commission%20has%20since%20been%20non-functional%2C%20leaving%20thousands%20of%20women%20without%20a%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20took%20charge%2C%20there%20were%2012%2C000%20cases%20pending.%20The%20court%20gave%20us%20the%20right%20to%20work%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20government%20locked%20us%20out%2C%20preventing%20us%20from%20doing%20our%20duty.%20Women%20are%20being%20tortured%2C%20and%20their%20right%20to%20justice%20has%20been%20taken%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shobha%20Ojha%2C%20a%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20chairperson%20of%20the%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20typically%20receives%20an%20average%20of%203%2C000%20complaints%20every%20year.%20With%20no%20one%20to%20address%20these%20grievances%2C%20the%20number%20of%20pending%20cases%20has%20ballooned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20across%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20suffering%20in%20silence%2C%20with%20no%20recourse%20to%20justice.%20Every%20day%2C%2028%20women%20and%20three%20girls%20go%20missing%20in%20the%20state.%20Between%20July%202021%20and%20May%2031%20this%20year%2C%2028%2C857%20women%20and%202%2C944%20girls%20were%20reported%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20ranks%20fifth%20in%20the%20country%20for%20crimes%20against%20women%2C%20with%2032%2C765%20FIRs%20registered%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20has%20sparked%20outrage%20among%20activists%20and%20legal%20experts.%20%26quot%3BIf%20cases%20are%20listed%20now%2C%20it%20will%20take%20seven%20more%20years%20to%20resolve%20them.%20The%20state%20must%20take%20immediate%20action%20to%20address%20this%20backlog%20and%20ensure%20justice%20for%20these%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sapna%20Sisodia%2C%20an%20advocate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShilpa%20Kaurav%2C%20the%20in-charge%20of%20the%20Mahila%20Police%20Station%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20has%20brought%20to%20light%20the%20significant%20challenges%20faced%20by%20women%20seeking%20justice%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20In%20a%20candid%20conversation%2C%20she%20highlighted%20the%20difficulties%20that%20arise%20when%20cases%20involving%20women's%20rights%20and%20safety%20are%20delayed%20or%20mishandled%20due%20to%20the%20inactivity%20of%20the%20Women's%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Kaurav%20explained%20that%20when%20a%20complaint%20is%20lodged%20with%20the%20State%20Women's%20Commission%20or%20even%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20the%20commission%20often%20requests%20reports%20from%20the%20police%20after%20conducting%20their%20investigation.%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20sometimes%20cases%20come%20to%20us%20where%2C%20if%20a%20complaint%20has%20been%20made%20in%20the%20State%20Women's%20Commission%20or%20even%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20they%20ask%20for%20a%20report%20from%20us%20after%20the%20investigation%2C%20or%20they%20also%20ask%20us%20for%20information%20to%20understand%20what%20action%20is%20being%20taken%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20mounting%20crisis%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20offered%20little%20reassurance.%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20the%20system%20is%2C%20it%20will%20be%20restructured%20according%20to%20the%20needs.%20The%20system%20will%20be%20made%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jagdish%20Devda%2C%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20offering%20a%20vague%20promise%20of%20future%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20State%20Women's%20Commission%20was%20formed%20in%201998%20with%20the%20mandate%20to%20safeguard%20women's%20rights%20and%20interests.%20The%20Commission%20has%20seven%20members%E2%80%94six%20non-governmental%20and%20one%20governmental%E2%80%94who%20hold%20ministerial%20status.%20However%2C%20with%20more%20than%2050%2C000%20complaints%20now%20packed%20away%20in%20dusty%20files%2C%20the%20Commission's%20very%20purpose%20is%20being%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724256660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fj6tthfso_mp-womens-commission_625x300_21_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-womens-panel-defunct-for-4-years-50-000-cases-pending-6387850%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20State%20Women's%20Commission%2C%20established%20to%20protect%20and%20empower%20women%2C%20has%20been%20left%20in%20a%20state%20of%20disarray%2C%20with%20more%20than%2050%2C000%20complaints%20pending%20and%20no%20one%20to%20hear%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Divers%20recovering%20bodies%20from%20superyacht%20at%20risk%20of%20'the%20bends'%20-%20why%20search%20has%20been%20so%20difficult%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724256300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F08%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-yacht-sicily-divers_6662583.jpg%3F20240821172514%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwhy-search-of-superyacht-wreck-has-been-so-difficult-13200804%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20search%20operation%20to%20find%20those%20missing%20after%20the%20sinking%20of%20the%20Bayesian%20superyacht%20has%20been%20plagued%20with%20difficulties.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A88%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwhy-search-of-superyacht-wreck-has-been-so-difficult-13200804%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwhy-search-of-superyacht-wreck-has-been-so-difficult-13200804%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwhy-search-of-superyacht-wreck-has-been-so-difficult-13200804%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Congressman%20Bill%20Pascrell%20dies%20at%2087%2C%20announce%20family%20on%20social%20media%22%2C%22content