V%20Wednesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20security%20officer%20named%20Khan%20was%20involved%20in%20this%20trafficking...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-the-rise-of-sandip-ghosh-and-how-doctor-rape-murder-put-him-under-scanner-6384587%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERise%20Of%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20And%20Spotlight%20Over%20Doctor%20Rape-Murder%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNext%2C%20illegal%20selling%20of%20bodies.%20The%20Forensic%20Medicine%20Head%20had%20complained...%20family%20members%20(of%20those%20whose%20bodies%20he%20allegedly%20sold)%20also%20complained.%20A%20national%20commission%20summoned%20him...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ali%20said%2C%20trailing%20off%2C%20suggesting%20nothing%20transpired%20of%20the%20summons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ali%20also%20accused%20Dr%20Ghosh%20of%20taking%20bribes%20of%2020%20per%20cent%20to%20award%20work%20orders%20or%20contracts%20and%20also%20deliberately%20failed%20students.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20like%20a%20mafia%20person...%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ali%20had%20said%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20these%20allegations%20I%20made...%20but%20no%20action%20was%20taken%20by%20authorities.%20Last%20night%20I%20went%20to%20a%20police%20station%20but%20they%20refused%20to%20accept%20a%20FIR%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20he%20had%20also%20filed%20a%20criminal%20case%20in%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20against%20Sandip%20Ghosh.%20That%20case%20may%20be%20heard%20tomorrow%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20rape-murder%