o%20fine-tune%20their%20invention%20and%20connect%20the%20device%20to%20an%20app.%20In%20a%20day%20and%20age%20when%20most%20seniors%20stay%20alone%2C%20it%20would%20be%20useful%20to%20alert%20their%20children%20or%20caregivers%20who%20stay%20far%20away%20by%20detecting%20problems%20early.%20It%20also%20has%20uses%20for%20doctors%20to%20monitor%20patients%20with%20known%20mobility%20issues.%20The%20device%20can%20monitor%20a%20patient%E2%80%99s%20condition%2C%20providing%20insights%20into%20their%20risk%20of%20falling%20and%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20their%20current%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahi%20and%20Hriday%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F343321%2Frahul-arepaka-harvested-robotics-hyderabad-ai-startup-laser-weeder-robot-help-farmers-earn-more%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etested%20the%20prototype%20on%20their%20grandparents%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20post%20which%20they%20tested%20it%20on%2050%20senior%20citizens%20living%20in%20old%20age%20homes.%20The%20physiotherapists%20validated%20their%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20efforts%20have%20not%20gone%20unnoticed%20%E2%80%94%20they%20qualified%20for%20the%20the%20IIT%20Tech%20Fest%2C%20IRIS%20National%20Fair%2C%20and%20the%20World%20STEM%20and%20Robotics%20Olympiad%20(WSRO)%20where%20they%20won%20the%20International%20Judges%20Choice%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20device%20will%20be%20priced%20between%20Rs%203%2C000%20and%20Rs%205%2C000%2C%20much%20lesser%20than%20current%20diagnostic%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20these%20young%20innovators%2C%20the%20project%20is%20not%20just%20about%20innovation%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20making%20a%20tangible%20difference%20in%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives.%20They%20want%20to%20prevent%20other%20grandparents%20from%20facing%20the%20issues%20as%20theirs%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Rahi%20Shah%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%2