g-production-expansion-with-centre-suzuki-motor-124082101144_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fmaruti-to-talk-cbg-production-expansion-with-centre-suzuki-motor-124082101144_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Experts%20Have%20Been%20Sent%20To%206%20High-Risk%20Glacial%20Lakes%20In%20Arunachal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20teams%20of%20experts%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20six%20high-risk%20glacial%20lakes%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20for%20the%20first%20time%20to%20assess%20the%20possibility%20of%20glacial%20lake%20outburst%20floods%20(GLOF)%20and%20the%20ways%20to%20access%20these%20water%20bodies%20for%20mitigation%20measures%2C%20official%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20lakes%20are%20located%20in%20the%20high%20altitude%20areas%20of%20Tawang%20and%20Dibang%20Valley%20districts%20-%20more%20than%2011%2C000%20feet%20above%20sea%20level%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teams%20will%20cover%20three%20high-risk%20glacial%20lakes%20each%20in%20Tawang%20and%20Dibang%20Valley%20out%20of%20the%2027%20high-risk%20lakes%20situated%20in%20five%20districts%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20as%20identified%20by%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%20(NDMA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20in%20Tawang%2C%20led%20by%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20Kanki%20Darang%2C%20left%20on%20August%2019%20to%20study%20the%20lake%20in%20Mago%20area%20in%20Thingbu%20circle%2C%20the%20sources%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20also%20cover%20two%20more%20lakes%20in%20Jang%20and%20Zemithang%20sub-divisions%20during%20the%20expedition%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20team%2C%20led%20by%20Dibang%20Valley%20District%20Disaster%20Management%20Officer%20Kabang%20Lego%2C%20left%20Anini%20to%20study%20two%20glacial%20lakes%20in%20Mipi%20circle%20which%20have%20been%20classified%20as%20'C'%20(low%20risk)%20by%20the%20NDMA%20and%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20create%20GLOF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20official%20sources%2C%20the%20expedition%20will%20likely%20take%2012%20days%20to%20complete%20the%20study%20on%20the%20first%20two%20lakes.%20Thereafter%2C%20the%20team%20will%20proceed%20to%20a%20high-risk%20glacial%20lake%20classified%20as%20'A'%20(high%20risk)%20in%20Etalin%20circle%2C%20sources%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teams%2C%20comprising%20experts%20from%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Mountaineering%20and%20Adventure%2C%20will%20carry%20out%20detailed%20studies%20on%20the%20accessibility%2C%20geo%20coordinates%2C%20lake%20boundary%2C%20area%2C%20elevation%2C%20habitations%20and%20point%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20will%20also%20analyse%20the%20land%20cover%20of%20the%20GLOF%20potential%20lakes%20to%20facilitate%20the%20Centre%20for%20Development%20of%20Advance%20Computing%20(C-DAC)%20and%20the%20Indian%20Meteorological%20Department%20to%20install%20automatic%20early%20warning%20systems%20and%20automatic%20weather%20stations%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20installation%20of%20these%20devices%20will%20likely%20help%20in%20averting%20high%20intensity%20damage%20to%20the%20lives%20and%20properties%20downstream%20of%20the%20lakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20is%20undertaken%20as%20a%20part%20of%20the%20initiatives%20undertaken%20by%20the%20NDMA%20after%20the%20catastrophic%20GLOF%20event%20in%20South%20Lhonak%20lake%20in%20Sikkim%20in%20October%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDMA%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20technical%20and%20research%20institutions%20of%20the%20country%2C%20has%20identified%20high-risk%20glacial%20lakes%20in%20the%20Himalayan%20region%20that%20could%20cause%20GLOF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%2027%20glacial%20lakes%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20high-risk%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20across%20five%20districts%20--%20Tawang%20(6)%2C%20Kurung%20Kumey%20(1)%2C%20Shi%20Yomi(1)%2C%20Dibang%20Vall