an%20tweakers%20in%20the%20three-match%20away%20ODI%20series%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20which%20they%20lost%200-2.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20India's%20first%20bilateral%20ODI%20series%20defeat%20against%20the%20Lankans%20in%2027%20years.%20%26quot%3BWe%20got%20undone%20against%20Sri%20Lanka.%20The%20mindset%20of%20India%20has%20been%20such%20that%20they've%20been%20so%20desperate%20to%20do%20well%20overseas%2C%26quot%3B%20Doeschate%20told%20Talksport%20Cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20focus%20has%20moved%20to%20doing%20well%20in%20Australia%20and%20England.%20We've%20kind%20of%20let%20playing%20spin%2C%20which%20was%20always%20a%20strength%20of%20the%20Indian%20team%2C%20fall%20back%20a%20little%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20one%20thing%20I'm%20looking%20forward%20to%20helping%20with%2C%20getting%20to%20that%20position%20where%20Indians%20are%20the%20best%20players%20of%20spin%20in%20the%20world%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Doeschate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20scheduled%20to%20face%20Bangladesh%20and%20New%20Zealand%20at%20home%20across%20five%20Test%20matches%20in%20September%20and%20October.%20Both%20these%20sides%20have%20handy%20spinners%20in%20their%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoeschate%2C%20a%20former%20Netherlands%20all-rounder%20with%20considerable%20coaching%20experience%20around%20the%20world%2C%20said%20playing%20spin%20is%20about%20making%20a%20mental%20shift%20rather%20than%20bringing%20about%20major%20technical%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20much%20of%20what%20we're%20going%20to%20bring%20is%20technical%20knowledge.%20It's%20more%20about%20mindsets%2C%20situational%20awareness%2C%20and%20how%20we%20think%20they%20can%20control%20certain%20phases%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20throw%20ideas%20out%20there...%20de-briefing%20and%20keeping%20the%20mental%20space%20really%20good.%20That's%20going%20to%20be%20really%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20elaborated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2044-year-old%20Dutchman%2C%20who%20will%20be%20assisting%20head%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%20along%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Abhishek%20Nayar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F974-abhishek-nayar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAbhishek%20Nayar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20the%20team%20is%20also%20desperate%20to%20win%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20(February%202025).%20With%20only%20three%20ODIs%20left%20in%20preparation%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20really%20challenging%20to%20switch%20between%20the%20formats%20and%20get%20the%20team%20ready%20for%20that%2C%20which%20again%20is%20something%20they're%20desperate%20to%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoeschate%20said%20qualifying%20for%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20(WTC)%20final%20in%20June%20next%20year%20is%20another%20important%20goal%20for%20Team%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20India%20are%20leading%20the%20WTC%20table%20with%20Australia%20in%20close%20pursuit%2C%20and%20Doeschate%20wanted%20to%20use%20the%2010%20Tests%20that%20India%20are%20scheduled%20to%20play%20to%20cement%20that%20position%20of%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20terms%20of%20what%20we're%20looking%20forward%20to...%20qualifying%20for%20the%20WTC%20final...%20there's%20a%20great%20opportunity%20with%2010%20Tests%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20five%20(Tests)%20in%20India%20and%20then%20we%20are%20going%20to%20Australia%20(for%20another%20five%20Tests)%2C%20which%20is%20going%20to%20be%20great.%26quot%3B%20Doeschate%20said%20walking%20into%20the%20Indian%20cricketing%20establishment%20was%20a%20daunting%20task%2C%20particularly%20after%20them%20winning%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20terms%20of%20timing%20(his%20appointment)%2C%20it's%20quite%20difficult%20to%20walk%20into%20a%20team%20that's%20just%20come%20back%20with%20the%20(T20)%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20in%20terms%20of%20what's%20ahead%20of%20us%20for%20the%20next%2018%20months%2C%20it's%20mouth-watering%20as%20a%20coach.%20It's%20all%20the%20series%20you%20want%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20and%20all%20the%20challenges%20you%20want%20to%20come%20up%20against%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724251200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F97ffvmo_indian-cricket-team_625x300_03_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Ffocus-has-moved-to-new-indian-cricket-team-coach-finds-shortcoming-in-rohit-sharma-and-cos-batting-6387229%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20is%20scheduled%20to%20face%20Bangladesh%20and%20New%20Zealand%20at%20home%20across%20five%20Test%20matches%20in%20September%20and%20October%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cholamandalam%20to%20raise%20Rs%201%2C000%20cr%20by%20selling%20largest%20private%20perp%20bond%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724250567000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-04%2F06%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1617718113-3494.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcholamandalam-to-raise-rs-1-000-cr-by-selling-largest-private-perp-bond-124082101106_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20note%2C%20which%20doesn't%20have%20a%20maturity%20date%2C%20is%20being%20arranged%20by%20Axis%20Bank%20Ltd.%20and%20carries%20a%20coupon%20of%209.50%20per%20cent%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20matter%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22c