0have%20instructed%20the%20police%20station%20to%20file%20FIRs%20against%20the%20identified%20troublemakers%20and%20send%20those%20who%20attempted%20to%20set%20the%20bus%20on%20fire%20to%20jail%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20town%20reported%20some%20incidents%20of%20violence%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Bandh%20call%20evoked%20a%20mixed%20response%20in%20Gopalganj.%20While%20some%20vehicles%20were%20seen%20on%20the%20road%2C%20some%20protesters%20caused%20disruptions%20along%20National%20Highway%2027%20and%20the%20railway%20tracks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharat%20Bandh%20was%20called%20by%20some%20Dalit%20organisations%20who%20took%20an%20opposing%20view%20to%20a%20recent%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%20by%20a%20seven-judge%20bench%20that%2C%20according%20to%20them%2C%20undermines%20the%20earlier%20ruling%20of%20a%20nine-judge%20bench%20in%20the%20landmark%20Indira%20Sawhney%20case%2C%20which%20established%20the%20framework%20for%20reservations%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724248260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F9gnpk838_bus-fire_625x300_21_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmob-tries-to-burn-bus-with-children-on-board-during-bharat-bandh-in-bihar-6386858%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20school%20bus%20with%20several%20children%20on%20board%20was%20saved%20from%20a%20potentially%20fatal%20attack%20by%20a%20group%20of%20people%20because%20of%20the%20timely%20intervention%20of%20police%20in%20Bihar's%20Gopalganj%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmob-tries-to-burn-bus-with-children-on-board-during-bharat-bandh-in-bihar-6386858%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%23FailedStatePakistan%20Trends%3A%20X%20Users%20React%20To%20What's%20Happening%20In%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20