owing%20concerns%20about%20the%20country's%20imminent%20collapse.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Ffailedstatepakistan-trends-x-users-react-to-whats-happening-in-pakistan-6386745%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Antitrust%20Body%20Warns%20Staff%20Over%20Unauthorised%20Media%20Contacts%2C%20Memo%20Shows%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20antitrust%20watchdog%20has%20warned%20staff%20in%20an%20internal%20memo%20not%20to%20share%20any%20information%20with%20the%20media%20when%20they%20are%20not%20authorized%20to%20do%20so%2C%20citing%20a%2060-year-old%20rule%20that%20prohibits%20such%20interactions%2C%20a%20document%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20observed%20that%20of%20late%20certain%20information%20related%20to%20the%20cases%20(under%20review)%20are%20published%2Favailable%20in%20the%20media%20...%20this%20has%20been%20viewed%20very%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Competition%20Commission%20of%20India%20(CCI)%20said%20in%20an%20Aug.%2020%20memo%20to%20all%20staff%2C%20which%20was%20seen%20by%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCI%20chairperson%20Ravneet%20Kaur%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Reuters%20queries%20on%20the%20memo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CCI%20is%20investigating%20high-profile%20companies%20and%20reviewing%20deals%20involving%20the%20likes%20of%20Amazon%2C%20Walmart's%20Flipkart%2C%20Reliance%2C%20Walt%20Disney%20and%20liquor%20maker%20Pernod%20Ricard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Reuters%20reported%20the%20CCI%20had%20reached%20an%20initial%20assessment%20that%20the%20%248.5%20billion%20Indian%20merger%20of%20Reliance%20and%20Disney%20media%20assets%20harms%20competition%20due%20to%20their%20power%20over%20cricket%20broadcast%20rights%2C%20and%20had%20been%20sent%20a%20warning%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20CCI%20also%20privately%20took%20an%20unusual%20step%20of%20recalling%20two%20reports%20that%20detailed%20alleged%20breaches%20of%20competition%20law%20by%20Apple%2C%20Reuters%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20internal%20CCI%20staff%20memo%20also%20said%20disciplinary%20action%20can%20be%20taken%20for%20non-compliance%20with%20the%20rules%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20also%20apply%20to%20officers%20even%20after%20they%20leave%20the%20CCI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20memo%20cited%20a%201964%20government%20rule%20that%20says%20%26quot%3Bno%20government%20servant%20shall%2C%20except%20in%20accordance%20with%20general%20or%20special%20order%20....%20communicate%2C%20directly%20or%20indirectly%2C%20any%20official%20document%20or%20any%20part%20thereof%20or%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724247420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fiaqh1qj_cci-_625x300_21_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Findia-antitrust-body-warns-staff-over-unauthorised-media-contacts-memo-shows-6386275%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20antitrust%20watchdog%20has%20warned%20staff%20in%20an%20internal%20memo%20not%20to%20share%20any%20information%20with%20the%20media%20when%20they%20are%20not%20authorized%20to%20do%20so%2C%20citing%20a%2060-year-old%20rule%20that%20prohibits%20such%20interactions%2C%20a%20document%20shows.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Findia-antitrust-body-warns-staff-over-unauthorised-media-contacts-memo-shows-6386275%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Diary%20Found%20Near%20Kolkata%20Doctor's%20Body%20Had%20Gold%20Medal%2C%20Top%20Hospitals'%20Dream%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20doctor%20w