2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fmfn64b8o_modi-poland_625x300_21_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20be%20in%20Poland%20and%20Ukraine%20this%20week.%20Both%20visits%20are%20historic%20in%20their%20own%20ways%3A%20for%20Poland%2C%20this%20will%20be%20the%20first%20visit%20by%20an%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20in%2045%20years%2C%20while%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20Modi's%20will%20be%20the%20first-ever%20visit%20by%20an%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister.%20Where%20Modi%20has%20talked%20about%20India%20and%20Poland's%20%26quot%3Bmutual%20commitment%20to%20democracy%20and%20pluralism%26quot%3B%20reinforcing%20the%20bilateral%20relationship%2C%20he%20has%20expressed%20%26quot%3Bhope%20for%20an%20early%20return%20of%20peace%20and%20stability%26quot%3B%20in%20Ukraine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20China%20and%20India%20are%20put%20in%20the%20same%20bracket%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20their%20response%20to%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%20But%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20the%20country%2C%20which%20follows%20his%20much-controversial%20trip%20to%20Russia%20last%20month%2C%20is%20why%20the%20world%20shouldn't%20compare%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20Is%20More%20Than%20Just%20A%20Mediator%20In%20Europe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi's%20visit%20to%20Russia%20last%20month%20raised%20a%20lot%20of%20eyebrows%20as%20it%20was%20also%20his%20first%20visit%20abroad%20in%20his%20third%20term.%20There%20is%20now%20talk%20of%20India%20becoming%20a%20potential%20peacemaker%20in%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war.%20But%20that%20is%20missing%20the%20woods%20for%20the%20trees.%20Modi%20will%20be%20in%20Ukraine%20to%20underline%20that%20New%20Delhi's%20position%20on%20the%20war%20remains%20consistent.%20Despite%20close%20ties%20with%20Russia%20and%20its%20decision%20not%20to%20publicly%20call%20out%20Russia%20as%20an%20aggressor%2C%20New%20Delhi%20has%20always%20maintained%20that%20the%20sanctity%20of%20territorial%20integrity%20and%20sovereignty%20remains%20inviolable%20in%20international%20affairs%2C%20and%20that%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20a%20sustainable%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20China%2C%20Modi%20publicly%20told%20Putin%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20Moscow%20that%20this%20was%20not%20the%20era%20of%20war%2C%20and%20expressed%20pain%20at%20the%20death%20of%20children%20after%20a%20lethal%20strike%20by%20Russia%20on%20Kyiv's%20main%20hospital%20for%20children.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20had%20denounced%20Modi%20for%20visiting%20Russia%2C%20calling%20the%20trip%20a%20%26quot%3Bdevastating%20blow%20to%20peace%20efforts%26quot%3B.%20But%20New%20Delhi%20has%20continued%20to%20maintain%20its%20ties%20with%20both%20Moscow%20and%20Kyiv%20throughout%20the%20course%20of%20the%20war%20over%20the%20last%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%2C%20steadfast%20in%20its%20belief%20that%20both%20sides%20should%20be%20engaged%20if%20a%20lasting%20solution%20is%20to%20be%20found.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Renewed%20Vision%20For%20Europe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEurope%20is%20facing%20a%20moment%20of%20reckoning%20with%20growing%20internal%20challenges%2C%20a%20widening%20regional%20divide%2C%20a%20war%20that%20shows%20no%20signs%20of%20ending%2C%20a%20rising%20China%2C%20calls%20for%20isolationism%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20a%20fracturing%20of%20the%20post-Cold%20War%20security%20arrangement.%20The%20end%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20will%20perhaps%20lay%20the%20foundations%20of%20a%20new%20security%20order%20in%20Europe%2C%20but%20that%20end%20is%20nowhere%20in%20sight%20as%20both%20sides%20search%20for%20favourable%20battlefield%20realities%20that%20they%20can%20potentially%20leverage%20at%20the%20negotiating%20table.%20It%20is%20at%20this%20critical%20juncture%20that%20Europe%20has%20started%20looking%20at%20India%20as%20a%20key%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20New%20Delhi%20has%20reciprocated.%20India%20now%20views%20Europe%20as%20central%20to%20its%20developmental%20and%20strategic%20priorities.%20This%20is%20borne%20by%20the%20extraordinary%20diplomatic%20investment%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20made%20in%20imparting%20momentum%20to%20its%20ties%20with%20Europe.%20What%20has%20been%20an%20evolving%20feature%20of%20this%20outreach%20is%20India's%20attempts%20to%20engage%20with%20different%20sub-regions%20of%20Europe%2C%20allowing%20New%20Delhi%20to%20focus%20on%20their%20core%20strengths.%20It%20is%20Central%20Europe%20that%20is%20now%20the%20focus%2C%20with%20Modi%20visiting%20Austria%20last%20month%20followed%20by%20Poland%20and%20Ukraine%20now.%20The%20region%20has%20developed%20its%20own%20unique%20voice%20on%20European%20matters%2C%20and%20especially%20after%20the%20Russian%20invasion%2C%20it%20has%20been%20critical%20in%20shaping%20the%20larger%20European%20response%20to%20regional%20and%20global%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Poland%20Matters%20To%20New%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20Poland%2C%20it%20is%20among%20the%20fastest-growing%20economies%20in%20Europe%20and%20has%20been%20vocal%20about%20its%20strategic%20aspirations%20to%20see%20Europe%20emerge%20as%20a%20key%20geopolitical%20actor%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%20Warsaw's%20role%20will%20also%20be%20critical%20in%20shaping%20the%20European%20security%20architecture%20once%20the%20embers%20of%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20cool%20down.%20Its%20location%20makes%20it%20a%20hub%20of%20connectivity%20across%20Europe%2C%20and%20India%20enjoys%20a%20lot%20of%20goodwill.%20If%20India%20is%20to%20move%20beyond%20France%2C%20Germany%20and%20the%20UK%20in%20its%20European%20imagination%2C%20then%20building%20strong%20economic%20ties%20with%20Poland%20will%20be%20critical.%20Modi's%20visit%20should%20lay%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%20long-term%20sustainable%20partnership%20with%20Warsaw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20New%