d%20during%20her%20swim%20was%20jellyfish.%20Hundreds%20of%20them%20stung%20her%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20already%20immense%20difficulty%20of%20the%20journey.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20very%20painful%3B%20I%20almost%20felt%20a%20shock%2C%20an%20electric%20current%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20my%20body%20to%20move%20for%20almost%2020%20minutes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20swimming%20for%20nearly%2011%20to%2012%20hours%2C%20the%20weather%20took%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worse%2C%20with%20high%20tides%20and%20strong%20currents%20making%20progress%20nearly%20impossible.%20Despite%20her%20continuous%20efforts%2C%20Tanvi%20found%20herself%20stuck%20in%20place.%20The%20observer%20on%20her%20support%20boat%20cautioned%20that%20crossing%20the%20channel%20would%20be%20difficult%20under%20such%20conditions.%20This%20treacherous%20region%20of%20the%20English%20Channel%20is%20notoriously%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98swimmer%E2%80%99s%20grave%E2%80%99%20due%20to%20its%20unforgiving%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20almost%20three%20hours%2C%20Tanvi%20was%20trapped%20in%20these%20relentless%20currents%2C%20her%20resilience%20tested%20to%20the%20limit.%20The%20situation%20grew%20even%20more%20daunting%20as%20three%20of%20her%20fellow%20swimmers%20were%20forced%20to%20abandon%20their%20attempts%20due%20to%20the%20worsening%20weather.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20waves%20were%20two%20to%20three%20metres%20in%20height%20and%20pulled%20you%20back%20to%20England.%20I%20was%20trapped%20in%20this%20and%20had%20to%20swim%20an%20extra%2010%20kilometres%20to%20reach%20the%20French%20coast%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tanvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Tanvi%20pressed%20on%20and%20covered%20the%20additional%2010%20kilometres%20due%20to%20the%20bad%20weather.%20When%20the%20observer%20asked%20if%20she%20wished%20to%20continue%2C%20it%20was%20an%20emphatic%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20actually%20wanted%20to%20give%20up.%20I%20had%20vomited%20and%20had%20zero%20energy.%