%20design%20in%20mind.%20But%20we%20have%20introduced%20them%20to%20cob%2C%20soil%20and%20other%20materials%20that%20could%20work%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20architect%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20tune%20with%20this%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20sat%20down%20with%20a%20bunch%20of%20architects%20who%20disproved%20the%20belief%20that%20cement%20is%20the%20only%20material%20suitable%20for%20construction.%20They%20believe%20it%20is%20time%20to%20do%20away%20with%20such%20ideals%20and%20make%20way%20for%20more%20planet-friendly%20perspectives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20architects%20in%20this%20piece%20converge%20on%20a%20verdict%20that%20responsible%20design%20and%20great%20aesthetics%20can%20indeed%20go%20hand-in-hand.%20Keeping%20conscious%20design%20at%20the%20fore%2C%20they%20are%20building%20a%20new%20India%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20is%20in%20tune%20with%20sustainability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20deep-dived%20into%20their%20projects%20and%20understood%20the%20ethos%20behind%20each%20material%20used.%20Here%20are%20five%20that%20impressed%20us%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Rammed%20earth%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20residence%20of%20Dr%20Achutshankar%20in%20Karyavattom%2C%20Kerala%2C%20always%20draws%20two%20glances%20from%20any%20onlooker.%20The%20first%20is%20because%20of%20its%20beautiful%2C%20rust-coloured%20exterior%20that%20perfectly%20compliments%20the%20mud%20on%20which%20it%20stands%2C%20and%20the%20second%20is%20because%20people%20can%20hardly%20believe%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335976%2Fmumbai-sustainable-home-ecofriendly-mud-architecture-geeli-mitti-ngo-lakhichand-jain%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estructure%20is%20built%20out%20of%20soil%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStanding%20proud%20of%20their%20creation%20are%20architect%20duo%20Guruprasad%20Rane%20and%20Manasi%20Puliyappatta%2C%20the%20brains%20behind%20the%20sustainable%20architecture%20firm%20%E2%80%98Bhoomija%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20use%20of%20rammed%20earth%20in%20the%20construction%2C%20Rane%20notes%20that%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20something%20novel.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20usage%20dates%20back%20to%20the%20Neolithic%20age.%20Recent%20demand%20for%20sustainable%20construction%20has%20led%20to%20renewed%20interest%20in%20this%20technique%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-1723551024.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20residence%20of%20Dr%20Achutshankar%20in%20Karyavattom%2C%20Kerala%20is%20built%20out%20of%20rammed%20earth%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-1723551024.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-1723551024-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-1723551024-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-1723551024-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-1723551024-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361157%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20residence%20of%20Dr%20Achutshankar%20in%20Karyavattom%2C%20Kerala%20is%20built%20out%20of%20rammed%20earth%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Guruprasad%20Rane%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20material%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Soil%2C%20sand%2C%20gravel%2C%20clay%2C%20and%20a%20stabiliser%20come%20together%20in%20a%20damp%20mixture%20to%20form%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F229955%2Fsustainable-architecture-startup-earth-building-mud-house-eco-friendly-ladakh-tamil-nadu-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erammed%20earth%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20that%20is%20moulded%20into%20the%20desired%20shape.%20For%20the%20residence%20in%20question%2C%20Rane%20says%20the%20soil%20was%20procured%20from%20a%2060%20cm%20depth%20and%20cleaned%20using%20a%20mechanised%20sieve%20to%20remove%20organic%20matter%20like%20roots%20and%20stones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20collective%20push%20encouraging%20the%20use%20of%20the%20material.%20Rane%20cites%20its%20abundance%20as%20the%20reason%20for%20this%20push.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20most%20cases%2C%20it%20is%20available%20on-site%20making%20this%20one%20of%20the%20most%20sustainable%20methods%20of%20construction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20The%20fact%20that%20it%20leaves%20no%20debris%20behind%20is%20another%20boon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20architects%20are%20often%20complimented%20on%20the%20timeless%20charm%20that%20the%20residence%20exudes.%20They%20credit%20the%20walls%20for%20this.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20breathable%20and%20porous%20because%20of%20the%20rammed%20earth%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rane%20points%20out.%20He%20adds%20that%20this%20quality%20also%20helps%20the%20home%20regulate%20its%20temperature%20and%20humidity%20levels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20March%202023%20research%20study%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EScience%20Direct%20%3C%2Fem%3Ealigns%20with%20what%20the%20architects%20claim.%20Underlining%20the%20advantages%20of%20using%20rammed%20earth%2C%20like%20the%20decrease%20in%20the%20environmental%20and%20economic%20costs%20related%20to%20transportation%2C%20the%20reduction%20in%20industrial%20processing%20required%2C%20and%20the%20material%E2%80%99s%20thermal-mass%20technology%2C%20the%20article%20is%20a%20nod%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F225624%2Fmumbai-architect-sustainable-homes-mud-cool-summer-ecofriendly-design-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ematerial%E2%80%99s%20sustainable%20quotient%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchitects%2C%20take%20notes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Having%20worked%20with%20rammed%20earth%20for%20multiple%20projects%2C%20Rane%20cautions%20architects%20who%20are%20planning%20on%20doing%20the%20same.%20%E2%80%9CPay%20attention%20to%20the%20soil%20composition%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20varies%20at%20different%20locations%20at%20the%20same%20site%3B%20the%20proportion%20of%20soil%20mix%20needs%20to%20be%20adjusted%20accordingly.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20roof%20overhangs%20should%20be%20installed%20around%20the%20homes%20made%20out%20of%20rammed%20earth%2C%20particularly%20those%20located%20in%20rainfall-prone%20regions.%20This%20is%20because%20the%20walls%20made%20of%20rammed%20earth%20need%20protection%20from%20the%20rain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Timber%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20team%20at%20SJK%20Architects%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Mumbai-based%20architectural%20firm%20that%20has%20spent%20the%20last%20three%20decades%20designing%20spaces%20%E2%80%94%20was%20approached%20with%20an%20ask%20to%20design%20a%20retirement%20home%20and%20skill%20centre%20in%20Awas%2C%20Alibaug%2C%20they%20were%20keen%20on%20it%20having%20a%20sustainable%20touch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETimber%20was%20the%20choice%20of%20material%20but%20not%20in%20its%20raw%20form.%20The%20architects%20decided%20to%20use%20Glue-Laminated%20Timber%20(GLT)%20and%20Cross-Laminated%20Timber%20(CLT)%20for%20the%20construction.%20These%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F231673%2Fmumbai-sustainable-home-no-air-conditioning-traditional-technique-palmyra-wood-ser106%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20engineered%20woods%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20say%2C%20see%20multiple%20layers%20of%20timber%20bonded%20together%20with%20durable%2C%20moisture-resistant%20structural%20adhesives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20material%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20What%20separates%20GLT%20from%20CLT%20is%20that%20in%20the%20former%2C%20laminates%20of%20structural%20timber%20are%20layered%20and%20glued%20in%20the%20same%20direction%2C%20on%20top%20of%20each%20other%2C%20while%20in%20CLT%2C%20each%20layer%20of%20timber%20is%20glued%20at%2090%20degrees%20to%20the%20layer%20above%20and%20below.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-1-1723551227.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20house%20at%20Awas%20in%20Alibaug%20was%20built%20using%20pre-engineered%20technology%20and%20timber%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-1-1723551227.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-1-1723551227-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-1-1723551227-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-1-1723551227-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-1-1723551227-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361161%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20house%20at%20Awas%20in%20Alibaug%20was%20built%20using%20pre-engineered%20technology%20and%20timber%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20SJK%20Architects%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20timber%20is%20wood%2C%20you%20point%20out.%20Is%20building%20with%20it%20sustainable%3F%20Sarika%20Shetty%2C%20one%20of%20the%20architects%20involved%20in%20the%20project%20responds%20by%20saying%20that%20this%20is%20where%20procurement%20comes%20into%20play.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20crucial%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20timber%20is%20sourced%20from%20certified%2C%20sustainably%20managed%20forests%2C%20even%20if%20it%20means%20sourcing%20from%20abroad.%20Utilising%20sea%20travel%20for%20transportation%20can%20significantly%20reduce%20emissions%20compared%20to%20air%20freight%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20research%20paper%20published%20in%202023%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F198111%2Fchennai-architect-sustainable-home-eco-friendly-construction-waste-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvantages%20of%20timber%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20assessed%20in%20comparison%20to%20its%20counterpart%20materials%20such%20as%20steel%20and%20concrete.%20The%20findings%20concluded%20that%20timber%20produces%20lower%20carbon%20emissions%20and%20has%20a%20lower%20environmental%20impact%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20other%20materials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20architects%20agree.%20Elaborating%20on%20the%20use%20of%20CLT%20and%20GLT%2C%20they%20share%20that%20these%20are%20carbon-negative%20(emit%20less%20than%20zero%20CO2%20equivalents)%20and%20thus%20renewable%2C%20provided%20the%20timber%20is%20sourced%20from%20sustainably%20managed%20forests.%20It%20is%20tolerant%20to%20warping%20and%20cracking%2C%20making%20it%20an%20excellent%20choice%20of%20material.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShetty%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20seen%20that%20CLT%20buildings%20have%20less%20than%20half%20of%20the%20embodied%20CO2%20of%20conventional%20reinforced%20concrete%20buildings.%E2%80%9D%20Their%20light%20weight%2C%20she%20says%2C%20reduces%20the%20foundations%E2%80%99%20overall%20weight%20and%20allows%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F309050%2Farchitect-quits-job-to-build-sustainable-earth-mud-homes-across-south-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeasier%20construction%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20handling%20and%20transportation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20perk%20is%20that%20CLT%20and%20GLT%20are%20made%20from%20softwoods.%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20they%20can%20be%20impregnated%20with%20chemicals%20to%20make%20the%20timber%20termite-proof%2C%20an%20advantage%20not%20typically%20found%20with%20hardwoods%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shetty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchitects%2C%20take%20notes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Shetty%20encourages%20architects%20to%20go%20in%20for%20species%20such%20as%20Douglas%20Fir%20and%20spruce%20pine%20fir%20which%20offer%20a%20lightweight%20alternative%20to%20traditional%20Indian%20hardwoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Ventilated%20terracotta%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPicture%20a%20construction%20material%20that%20keeps%20the%20structure%20cool%20in%20the%20peak%20of%20Indian%20summers%2C%20provides%20acoustic%20insulation%20(cuts%20noise%20levels%20by%20up%20to%2015%20percent)%20and%20looks%20pretty!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchitects%20of%20firm%20GPM%20Architects%20and%20Planners%20were%20as%20amazed%20as%20you%20are%20when%20they%20worked%20with%20ventilated%20terracotta%20tiles%20to%20design%20the%20Defence%20Office%20complexes%20in%20KG%20Marg%20and%20Africa%20Avenue%2C%20Delhi.%20If%20you%20pass%20by%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20agree.%20The%20campus%20makes%20for%20a%20beautiful%20tapestry%20with%20the%20terracotta%20tiles%20stealing%20the%20limelight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20how%20the%209.60%20lakh%20sq%20ft%20area%20was%20completed%20in%2010%20months%20using%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F271590%2Fman-builds-low-cost-ecofriendly-home-from-village-scrap-waste%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epre-engineered%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20architects%20say%20the%20terracotta%20made%20it%20easy.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-2-1723551495.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ventilated%20terracotta%20makes%20for%20a%20great%20material%20that%20provides%20thermal%20and%20acoustic%20insulation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-2-1723551495.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-2-1723551495-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-2-1723551495-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-2-1723551495-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-2-1723551495-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361163%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVentilated%20terracotta%20makes%20for%20a%20great%20material%20that%20provides%20thermal%20and%20acoustic%20insulation%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20GPM%20Architects%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20you%20know%20the%20material%E2%80%99s%20use%20traces%20back%20to%20the%20Harappan%20Civilisation%20(3300-1300%20BC)%3F%20A%202024%20research%20study%20published%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EInternational%20Journal%20of%20Novel%20Research%20and%20Development%3C%2Fem%3E%20highlighted%20the%20eco-benefits%20of%20terracotta%20pointing%20to%20its%20energy%20efficiency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20firing%20process%20used%20in%20terracotta%20production%20typically%20requires%20lower%20temperatures%20compared%20to%20other%20ceramics%20and%20building%20materials%20like%20concrete%20or%20metals.%20It%20has%20reduced%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20paper%20noted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1723551751.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20terracotta%20tiles%20make%20for%20a%20beautiful%20design%20against%20the%20landscape%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1723551751.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1723551751-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1723551751-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1723551751-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1723551751-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361167%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20terracotta%20tiles%20make%20for%20a%20beautiful%20design%20against%20the%20landscape%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20GPM%20Architects%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20material%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20architects%20behind%20this%20construction%20concede%20that%20ventilated%20terracotta%20tiles%20are%20low-maintenance%20materials.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20reducing%20solar%20heat%20gain%2C%20decreasing%20the%20air%20conditioning%20load%2C%20they%20save%20up%20to%2030%20percent%20energy%20costs.%E2%80%9D%20Because%20of%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F56836%2Faluminium-foil-insulation-in-summer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethermal%20insulation%20capabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20terracotta%20tiles%20reduce%20heat%20transfer%20into%20the%20building%2C%20thus%20maintaining%20a%20stable%20indoor%20temperature.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMade%20from%20clay%2C%20which%20is%20naturally%20available%20in%20abundance%2C%20terracotta%20has%20a%20low%20carbon%20footprint%20and%20is%20recyclable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchitects%2C%20take%20notes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Ensure%20that%20the%20material%E2%80%99s%20thermal%20insulation%20aligns%20with%20local%20conditions%2C%20architects%20say.%20Sharing%20some%20precautionary%20advice%2C%20they%20say%20that%20terracotta%20adds%20to%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20facade.%20Hence%20structural%20support%20is%20essential.%20They%20also%20pointed%20out%20how%2C%20in%20this%20particular%20design%2C%20adding%20proper%20ventilation%20behind%20the%20cladding%20went%20a%20long%20way%20to%20prevent%20moisture%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20DGU%20glass%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20marker%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F56423%2Fthis-eco-friendly-house-decor-goals%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egood%20aesthetics%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20how%20architect%20Vineeta%20Singhania%20Sharma%20of%20Confluence%20%E2%80%94%20an%20architectural%20firm%20founded%20in%201999%20%E2%80%94%20describes%20this%20material.%20It%20formed%20one%20of%20the%20principal%20elements%20in%20the%20design%20of%20the%20Food%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20Authority%20of%20India%20(FSSAI)%20office%20at%20Indirapuram.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPicture%20two%20panes%20of%20glass%20filled%20with%20a%20buffer%20of%20air%20in%20between.%20This%20is%20how%20the%20material%20appears.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20material%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20use%20of%20the%20DGU%20(Double%20Glazed%20Unit)%20glass%20in%20the%20office%20space%20optimises%20the%20daylight%2C%20allowing%20natural%20light%20to%20penetrate.%20Sharma%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20%5BDGU%20Glass%5D%20has%20excellent%20thermal%20insulation%20properties%20and%20maintains%20a%20more%20stable%20internal%20temperature%2C%20reducing%20the%20reliance%20on%20heating%20and%20cooling%20systems.%20This%20leads%20to%20significant%20energy%20savings%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331901%2Fcouple-quit-job-to-build-eco-friendly-carbon-negative-home-homestay-in-himachal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elower%20carbon%20footprint%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1723551625.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DGU%20Glass%20forms%20a%20major%20component%20of%20the%20architecture%20at%20the%20FSSAI%20office%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1723551625.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1723551625-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1723551625-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1723551625-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1723551625-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361165%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDGU%20Glass%20forms%20a%20major%20component%20of%20the%20architecture%20at%20the%20FSSAI%20office%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Confluence%20Consultancy%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20insulation%20capacity%20extends%20to%20noise%20too.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20particularly%20beneficial%20in%20urban%20areas%20or%20near%20busy%20roads%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchitects%2C%20take%20notes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Since%20the%20material%20works%20to%20insulate%20spaces%2C%20the%20climate%20of%20the%20region%20needs%20to%20be%20kept%20in%20mind.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20structural%20considerations%20need%20to%20be%20made%20to%20ensure%20the%20building%20can%20support%20the%20weight%20and%20thickness%20of%20DGU%20glass%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sharma.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Clay%20bricks%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20of%20American%20architect%20Louis%20Kahn%20was%20considered%20edifying%20by%20devotees%20of%20sustainable%20architecture.%20The%20imprints%20of%20his%20design%20philosophies%20are%20in%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%20at%20Ahmedabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20acclaimed%20for%20his%20abstract%20constructions%20that%20featured%20vast%20brick%20walls%20and%20geometric%20voids%2C%20and%20his%20ability%20to%20capitalise%20on%20the%20Sun%E2%80%99s%20shadows.%20It%20is%20with%20Kahn%E2%80%99s%20architectural%20mindset%20in%20view%2C%20that%20architects%20Amit%20Khanna%2C%20Ankita%20Misra%2C%20and%20Krishna%20Yadav%20of%20Amit%20Khanna%20Design%20Associates%20(AKDA)%20have%20