20felt%20responsible%20as%20a%20citizen.%20Otherwise%2C%20Bengaluru%20would%20become%20like%20any%20other%20Indian%20city.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20regret%20later%20that%20I%20could%20have%20done%20something%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20began%20visiting%20government%20offices%20to%20understand%20his%20role%20and%20capacity%20as%20a%20citizen.%20In%202007%2C%20he%20started%20planting%20saplings%20on%20weekends.%20Every%20year%2C%20more%20and%20more%20people%20began%20joining%20him%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20SayTrees%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kapil%20aims%20to%20restore%2015%20more%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20Chennai%2C%20and%20Hyderabad%20before%20the%20next%20monsoon.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-800x800.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-600x600.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-1723177895-400x400.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2F8-3_11zon-17